{"tid":1688731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【有圖】燒傷後的正確護理（重post求推）","createTime":"2019-11-02T14:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T23:21:30.000Z","uid":257533,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6f417490443496d306330d5caa54515e243385ec","tid":1688731,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CriVyFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCriVyFE.png&h=2c0afe8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpoN9d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpoN9d0.png&h=520ae7e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係護士<br />\n<br />\n我中意處理傷口，因為成功感明顯。<br />\n年頭我心急大意，一野打開個蒸爐，<br />\n就將自己手腕燒傷。<br />\n其傷口都將我身邊人嚇親。<br />\n作為護士，當然學以至用，目標：不留痕，最快復元。<br />\n<br />\nDay0: 事發當日，真係痛到訓都辛苦，舒緩燙傷既痛，冰敷係最易做到，小林退熱貼都唔work, 都最後都係冰敷。<br />\n只要加多條毛巾，就唔怕整濕床。<br />\n痛得緊要，我拎左2種藥黎食。<br />\nTramadol 50mg一日兩次<br />\nPanadol 1000mg一日四次<br />\n(我食到最大dose架啦，唔可以再食更多，而且我只食左1日) <br />\n<br />\nDay1:訓醒都仲有痛，但明顯減少。第二日返教會，貼小林退熱貼都可以舒緩到下。不過其實唔郁最好，因為開始發現出水泡，穿左就有機會傷口感染。我既不留痕目標就會因為穿左，而極大機會失敗。<br />\n<br />\nDay2-6:由好痛到漸漸唔痛，水泡由好脹，到開始消。<br />\n我只係做2樣野。<br />\n1. 當傷口係塊面咁，瘋狂保濕。一d都唔慳咁將d保濕精華如mask般敷燒傷位置。平靚正可選蘆薈。<br />\n(大前題冇傷口，水泡冇穿冇爛) <br />\n2. 維他命c, 加快新陳代謝，快快更新我d皮膚。<br />\n<br />\nDay7-8: 鮮紅位置漸退，死皮變黑，慢慢變乾。但鮮紅位置仍有少少痛。依舊只做兩件事，補濕同維他命c.<br />\n<br />\nDay 9-14: 死皮開始甩，然後我又手痕去r...結果其實唔算甩得靚。<br />\n<br />\nDay14: 我見甩哂都冇野影，就冇再影。個陣係仲會擔心自己手痕r完，會唔會好返都有個印。<br />\n<br />\nNow: 除左條青根依舊明顯，其實根本睇唔出痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n謝袮讓我有知識<br />\n願我護理的不只表面傷口<br />\n希望我這小傷，能幫助燒傷的人"},{"pid":"bcd3b00a2fa7d9a7ed0c2999faeecc5a85198545","tid":1688731,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:13:46.000Z","msg":"[賣港賊之一]如果連CCTVB都入唔到制裁名單 抗爭？不了<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1688660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1688660</a>"},{"pid":"b421ed852f365da191d37ae84b433b67a9a9ab70","tid":1688731,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"幫推，見到都覺得痛"},{"pid":"7c9fb5dabb3b4b86a9ef8b52ff8d468d158bb1a9","tid":1688731,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"如果你班mon po狗仲自認係白警 點解要剝削被捕者嘅權利?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1688681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1688681</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曱甴王 甴近平 江甴文 毛甴東 習曱甴"},{"pid":"cb2aa530af6ddb83bfc48ee773dcc9c52c0e129f","tid":1688731,"uid":74146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"其實死皮多手走去meat走會唔會傷口感染/ 易留疤？我成日都仆親好似有你呢啲傷口都會多手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e210963c9956bdec5d3595d23cf6e7679c44477","tid":1688731,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"Tramadol 藥房有冇架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎屋企藥箱要入定貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14a07b71814cee6eb1184ddc379e8e43117f8aa","tid":1688731,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"維仔命C係食定茶 幾多mg<br />\n另外保濕想請問用邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c71f039ee94006f9bf0bcaa02395a2917408636","tid":1688731,"uid":186171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"f74be8f885c8b537d78c03ecccc15dffbaeb83da","tid":1688731,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"panadol 1000mg 一日四次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真咩"},{"pid":"1fcf1a08039ec5d63d2d92099cc65a52a69ca35d","tid":1688731,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9104895229d3ecc20a35117c0f93fe077487b56e","tid":1688731,"uid":58991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"6e11c15ce25786bbed03fa1dbc8532616adcb9de","tid":1688731,"uid":269216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"我試過隻腳二級燒傷，個水泡穿撚左，然後發炎，最後要去診所噴啲凍凍地嘅野麻痺隻腳小小感覺，個醫生幫我挖開個傷口&quot;kim&quot;入面啲濃出黎...到而家已經過左我諗over 五年，個印仍然望落好清晰，我諗佢會跟住我一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca649386ba273ac28cf19a7ee4f701a1a83f384","tid":1688731,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6871d34ea9fa6776672c1de54e494ceb3d9358","tid":1688731,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"1. 一開頭受傷嗰時一定要用大量水沖洗，沖幾個字<br />\n係咪生理鹽水都唔緊要，因為降温最緊要<br />\n之後先用番無菌技術嚟處理傷口<br />\n唔好搽任何嘢<br />\n一開頭千其唔好用冰，因為血管收縮咗仲難散熱<br />\n2. 樓主嘅燒傷都好淺，&lt;1% 又係第一程度<br />\n但如果傷口大/有水泡/甩皮，最好真係睇醫生<br />\n因為好易細菌感染<br />\n3. 睇醫生唔洗講自己點燒傷，人哋最多問你受傷嘅mechanism（火？電？水？），你鳩噏都吹你唔脹"},{"pid":"530e168e47e9d2e59157376270d4bbaab3b3420d","tid":1688731,"uid":8207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"running water 沖係基本喎<br />\n你無沖？<br />\n冰敷有時限但沖水可以一路沖<br />\n同埋tramadol 平常人點有啊？？？"},{"pid":"d90e48ccdd1dece062c962261b28cb2237cb8a2f","tid":1688731,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e210963c9956bdec5d3595d23cf6e7679c44477","tid":1688731,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"Tramadol 藥房有冇架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎屋企藥箱要入定貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"Tramadol 要醫生處方"},{"pid":"6036a6bf7426d4efb9fa4aca838b0206ee0bff86","tid":1688731,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d90e48ccdd1dece062c962261b28cb2237cb8a2f","tid":1688731,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e210963c9956bdec5d3595d23cf6e7679c44477","tid":1688731,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"Tramadol 藥房有冇架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎屋企藥箱要入定貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"Tramadol 要醫生處方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"有啲藥房嚴啲，有啲。。。"},{"pid":"643e33d1ed850d4fea3de10e78b2c17847069f51","tid":1688731,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14a07b71814cee6eb1184ddc379e8e43117f8aa","tid":1688731,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"維仔命C係食定茶 幾多mg<br />\n另外保濕想請問用邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"維他命c,  食既<br />\n唔可以塗係傷口，痛死"},{"pid":"95147f93e361d5140b91fe7f119b3826f5f84695","tid":1688731,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"530e168e47e9d2e59157376270d4bbaab3b3420d","tid":1688731,"uid":8207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"running water 沖係基本喎<br />\n你無沖？<br />\n冰敷有時限但沖水可以一路沖<br />\n同埋tramadol 平常人點有啊？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"我有沖水，但都會心痛自己屋企水費，同埋沖左幾個鐘，而且夜啦，好眼訓，所以先諗方法舒服d訓。"},{"pid":"4d7698930731c308f1d46c73da86c18f666026c8","tid":1688731,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f74be8f885c8b537d78c03ecccc15dffbaeb83da","tid":1688731,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"panadol 1000mg 一日四次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"Panadol一日四次，每次1000mg<br />\n認真！我真係丁點痛都忍唔到。"},{"pid":"956e721ebbc44bd79d646180f8aafbdeac1dde16","tid":1688731,"uid":310805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T23:21:30.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n<br />\n燒傷真係要小心護理"}]}